==English==

===Verb===
{{en-verb|ghostwrites|ghostwriting|ghostwritten}}

# {{intransitive}} To write under the name of another (especially [[literary]] works).
#: ''Maria '''ghostwrites''' for a living and finds it a thankless task.''
# {{transitive}} To [[author]] a literary work or [[speech]] in the place of another.
#: ''Bob '''ghostwrote''' the president's address.''

